Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Kojirō was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:26.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,I do not need sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:30.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Adding sugar to coffee is a heresy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:31.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:44.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mocha is great as always. The feeling of soft and good flavor filling my mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:51.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt your rest, but did you see this guy around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Isn't this Musashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:58.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Well... kind of. Did he do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:04.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes. Sējūrō, our head at Yoshioka, was hit on his head by him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! Musashi took down the head of Yoshioka Dōjō?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh! Are you understanding our mortification?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. I never thought the head of Yoshioka was that weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:21.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,If that was the case, I could have taken him down first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,My hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:44.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn Musashi! That weak but lucky bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:49.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryoma, where are you taking me to-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:52.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,The hideout for making the new Jipangu State.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:57.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? While I like what you're doing, I don't want to be a comrade of a villain-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:04.71,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\fs52\pos(388,168)\c&H000000&\3c&HF0F0CD&}TEA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:03.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,I like how you're upfront with what you're thinking, no matter what it's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,I finally found you, Ryoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,This my hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:15.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh, it's pretty small for a hideout of making a new Jipangu State-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're very outspoken guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Anyway, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:30.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,We must report back to our master Denshichirō right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:36.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought making a new Jipangu State would involve preparing for a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:39.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,It looks like you're in a commerce-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:47.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's right. I'm doing this on purpose. Money is more realistic than fighting to make a new country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,What do you sell-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,I sell peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:53.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:58.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right. We give food to a country with famine, and prepare to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:03.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,help people living in villages that became battlefields.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:07.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is that what it takes to make a new Jipangu State-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:11.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now, Musashi, do you know why they fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:12.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,They are fighting because there are not enough resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,If everyone could have anything they want...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:21.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,They will live without fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:52.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's what I am talking about. The Jipangu State that I'm dreaming for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:56.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,is the place where everything is enough and no fight occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:19:00.03,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an5\frz-88.5\fs40\t(0,3440,\fs53)\pos(349,290)\fax-0.1\3c&H8DB6D7&\c&H000000&}Shinsen Family House
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:19:00.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,What? You found Ryoma's hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:04.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,I saw him entering a farmhouse close to the Miyako Palace with my bare eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:07.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Great. I will show him my wrath this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:10.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Let's go!\N-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Everyone! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:16.25,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs48\pos(531,151)\frz-92\frx1\fax0.3\3c&HC0FBF8&\c&H000000&}Yoshioka Dōjō Inc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,That brat is definitely at a farmhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:18.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Understood? We must catch him as of today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,I entrust you on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryoma, you look like you're enjoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:29.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,I wonder if you want to be my comrade, Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:34.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,But still... I must become the number one Karakuri martial artist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:42.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I manage to become the number one martial artist, I will marry Otsuru-{\i0}dasu{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:51.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,I still must aim for the number one Karakuri martial artist-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:56.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see. If you're that determined, you just gotta push the limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:20:01.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Even though our dreams are different, let's do our best for the objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:03.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:07.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:10.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,Someone has come near to our hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,I found you, Ryoma! You're not running away from me this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:21.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,I still have a lot to do. I am not intending to be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:29.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now! Let's run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:36.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, Musashi! I will have revenge on you for my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:39.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,You didn't need to come in time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:44.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Here they are!\N-It seems that Shinsen family followed us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ryoma! Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ryoma! Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am not Ryoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,This way! Chase him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're not running away any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,You call this running away-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Since I can't fight as freely there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:11.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,I just changed the place-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,What the? He's not Ryoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.82,0:21:15.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where is Ryoma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ryoma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:32.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn you, Ryoma! When did you come out with that?! Come back here, you coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:34.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Come up with something else than walking, Kondō.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:40.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,Even though I am called a coward, I'm not dying until I achieve what I dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:48.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ryoma! I finally understood-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:51.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:56.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Final blow! Extreme forward rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:02.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you running away, Musashi? Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:06.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Running away is a tactic-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:14.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, see you soon! The dawn of Jipangu State is soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:20.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Meeting with Ryoma, a wind-like Karakuri man, has let Musashi take a big step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.53,0:22:25.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Run, Musashi! Until the day that your dreams come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:45.42,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Sometimes the moon jumps over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:48.67,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,the pocket of empty sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:51.05,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Laugh loudly and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.68,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,morning will come tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:59.02,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about losing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.02,0:23:02.61,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Keep going! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.02,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,A bare hand is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:15.12,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:23.17,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how life is! Look, a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:27.88,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,follows us wagging its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:38.81,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:47.28,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how the future is, too! Look, tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:53.11,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,is opening its hands and smiling at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:09.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,After the painful training, I am supposed to be a martial artist worth of one's salt,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.52,0:24:11.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,but I still don't have the crucial sword-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:15.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Because of that I went to meet the master of sword craftsman, I was refused-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:21.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn! If he's not going to make me one, I'm going to make one myself-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
